review: I bought this for my brother for a Christmas gift when we got him a guitar. He never used it, but not because of anything to do with the actual product
It came and it wasn't broken or bad and it held my brother's guitar for a few years until he sold it
These are guitar picks and I don't play guitar so I can't say much more than the fact that they came and they were what they said they were
This is a fine bag for a guitar, I got it for my brother...I'm not a music person but its good
I can't say anything bad for it because I don't know much about it other than the fact that it works
